User Story12345:
Searching a user in HRMS Website
When we need verification/ validation we need to use Then, there can be multiple Then in a one scenario.
Search by ID:
Given user navigates to HRMS application
When user enters valid username and password
And User clicks on login button
Then user navigates to dashboard page
When user clicks on PIM option
And User clicks on employee information button
When user enters employee ID
And User clicks on search button
Then user see employee information is displayed

Search by Name:
Given user navigates to HRMS application
When user enters valid username and password
And User clicks on login button
Then user navigates to dashboard page
When user clicks on PIM option
And User clicks on employee information button
When user enters valid employee Name
And User clicks on search button
Then user see employee information is displayed
